{"data":[{"id":561918668,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"998b89ad5b72d3478debe4bf99c08bae","url_token":"stanly-25","name":"Stanly","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/21b0d508fcebd55e5388b7a091b19985_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/21b0d508fcebd55e5388b7a091b19985_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/998b89ad5b72d3478debe4bf99c08bae","user_type":"people","headline":"游手好闲","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561918668","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546014576,"updated_time":1546014669,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e从你用“哥德巴赫猜想”这六个字作标题就知道你不可能证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e流量至上的年代数学王冠上的明珠竟然也要被沽名钓誉之徒拿来玷污。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不知道你发这个问题的目的是什么，也不知道为什么莫名其妙的上了热搜，连着三天不停地推送。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我从省重点高中的实验班毕业考上的大学，班级里边百分之八十的人都参加竞赛，能得数学一等奖的同学实力我相当清楚，不要说高中数学，即便是我学到博士，高等数学，高等代数，泛函分析，图论基础相关的课程我全都学过我仍然是连证明哥德巴赫猜想的边都碰不到。我希望你是真的证明了成功了，如果仅仅像民科一样“自圆其说”，便是对踏踏实实走过来的一众学子的侮辱，让知乎成千上万的人陪你玩这种弱智游戏，对于科学和知识如此的不严肃不尊重只能感叹世风日下令人不齿。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看看费马大定理的证明过程。总结前人工作是基础，在此之上需要一位至少也是万中无一的天才花费数年时间整理当下数学各个分支所能用到的工具，再花费数年的时间刻苦钻研，在此过程中也需要不断的与同行大牛们交流学习新想法，期待着一生可能仅有一次的“灵光乍现”突破问题的关键创立一套新方法新理论，甚至一个新的数学分支，再与几位同行不断完善证明。有些人甚至花了一辈子也仅能为问题证明做出一点点贡献。上面的这些必要条件你具备几点？这种难度的问题，你一拍脑瓜说自己证明了，我是真的不信！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560785004,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560785004","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545887673,"updated_time":1545887673,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我不想说别的，只希望题主把前面的高赞回答一字一句认真看完。大家没有在指责他，也很少有人在使用网络暴力。这是他应该经历的一堂来自知友的课。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560785999,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"370b088f3d34a08db9296a3106c65a00","url_token":"flamepig","name":"FLAMEPIG","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8dfd3dfc8b080f2966412a29a78b4aa7_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8dfd3dfc8b080f2966412a29a78b4aa7_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/370b088f3d34a08db9296a3106c65a00","user_type":"people","headline":"不乱于心 不役于物 不困于情","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560785999","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-110439db7900c40979540778c4ec2c86_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545887760,"updated_time":1545887760,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e大家好，我是一个初中生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想问如果我证明了哥德巴赫猜想，我能保送重点高中吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e