p\u003e费玉清就说他有个小技巧，平时练习试着拿舌头去触玻璃杯的杯底，长期练下来有利于舌头的发声。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb076091e004cbd2fa896ef1d7d693f8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"860\" data-rawheight=\"925\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb076091e004cbd2fa896ef1d7d693f8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"860\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb076091e004cbd2fa896ef1d7d693f8_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='860'%20height='925'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"860\" data-rawheight=\"925\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb076091e004cbd2fa896ef1d7d693f8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"860\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb076091e004cbd2fa896ef1d7d693f8_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb076091e004cbd2fa896ef1d7d693f8_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e对，就是上面这种很深口的玻璃杯。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是这个同学是个死脑筋，非要接着问：“那么如果我有一天练到舌头能够贴住杯底了，那时候该怎么继续练唱歌呢？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“你都能把舌头碰到杯底了，还唱什么歌呢！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“你都能证哥德巴赫猜想了，还读什么清北呢！”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559980117,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"afa53fcc789231cf7c5f0f331495a258","url_token":"xiao-yu-93-20-67","name":"打脸","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3e1c2a2f1908cd508ccdf6277b3dc0a3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3e1c2a2f1908cd508ccdf6277b3dc0a3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/afa53fcc789231cf7c5f0f331495a258","user_type":"people","headline":"学生 发动机","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559980117","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545798744,"updated_time":1545798805,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我刚开始看见这个问题的时候，他只有6个关注，我呵呵一笑，觉得他骗关注没有成功。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e结果过了两天，就有2.1k关注了，真的是啪啪打得脸疼啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大佬，我1月1号零点不看地球最后的夜晚了，您教教我微积分b怎么上九十吧，该期末了，挺急的。像您这样的大佬，教教我肯定只要几分钟，谢谢了!\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563909034,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3c5c87d666bcf685612efd306620c565","url_token":"xiao-chun-ji-62-31","name":"小纯洁","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5a889e3c73acec4adad18f171c0f4aba_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5a889e3c73acec4adad18f171c0f4aba_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3c5c87d666bcf685612efd306620c565","user_type":"people","headline":"Please call me Mr.Chun","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563909034","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546310177,"updated_time":1546310177,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e数学奖，必须是诺贝尔的。没有让他们给你办一个\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562831438