:1546158828,"updated_time":1546158828,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我家孩子这学期上语文课有篇课文很让我感触，共勉：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e青蛙坐在井里。小鸟飞来了，落在井沿上。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e青蛙问小鸟：“你从哪儿来呀？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e小鸟回答说：“我从天上来，飞了一百多里，口渴了，下来找点儿水喝。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e青蛙说：“朋友，别说大话了！天不过井口那么大，还用飞那么远吗？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e小鸟说：“你弄错了。天无边无际，大得很哪！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e青蛙笑了，说：“朋友，我天天坐在井里，一抬头就能看见天。我不会弄错的。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e小鸟也笑了，说：“朋友，你是弄错了。不信，你跳出井来看一看吧。”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561266688,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561266688","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545938060,"updated_time":1545977734,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不……你可以得诺贝尔数学奖。(手动狗头\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560044311,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0dc28834679eba40c6b827a4cd6088ee","url_token":"qin-shi-zun-98","name":"秦世尊","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0dc28834679eba40c6b827a4cd6088ee","user_type":"people","headline":"大学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560044311","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545804444,"updated_time":1545804444,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我也证明出来了歌德巴赫猜想，等一月一日我看看咱俩方法一不一样\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560676853,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4e2084aaf135ac92452c54bfc52a485a","url_token":"yu-qi-qi-64-30","name":"居居蓝","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6984f7b052d1a749417bf40eb642c749_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6984f7b052d1a749417bf40eb642c749_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4e2084aaf135ac92452c54bfc52a485a","user_type":"people","headline":"不胖到120斤不换签名","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560676853","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545878717,"updated_time":1545966723,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e手痒来答一发。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e短短几天，眼睁睁地看着吃瓜群众的数量从几十个变成了几W个……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b11444181781a29441692bba18041110_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b11444181781a29441692bba18041110_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e从现有的回答看，98%的人都持怀疑看法，表示从未见过逼乎下的回答态度如此一致。。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePS :  这个问题简直我的快乐源泉，工作学习累了就来看看最新回答，哈哈。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么这个问题为啥能激起大家的g点呢，\u003cb\u003e因为短短一句话的问题，有三个关键点，高中生，哥猜，清华保送。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e先说下哥猜。\u003c/b\u003e  本人文科数学渣，所以对数学知识的认识止步于高中。前几天才知乎刷到了这个问题，阅读一些数学大佬的回答后，对哥猜这个定理不明觉厉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e再说高中\u003c/b\u003e。。我们不妨来假设一下，如果提问者没有说自己证明了这个定理，只是以一个高中生对高等数学的好奇，和求学途径的一种可能在知乎发问，那么现在回答中冷嘲热讽的比例至少少一半。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么回答中有人会热心普及哥猜这个定理的证明难度，有人会欣赏年轻人初生牛犊不怕虎的样子像极了自己当年，鼓励他保持求知欲，继续学习研究……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e但提问者信誓旦旦地说已经证毕，还自信地说没有任何漏洞，1月1日欢迎观看，这味道就不一样了。不啻在质疑数学界的权威性…\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有句话叫  无知者无畏，我觉得挺符合他现在这种情况的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e各种可能大家都说的很全面了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e现在我们总结下大致有这样几种观点：\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e1.提问者是个只有初等数学程度的高中生。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学成绩和智商优于同学，但对哥猜知其然而不知所以然。所以“以为”自己已经证明出，想走捷径求学；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e2.提问者是个民科数学家。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e开了个昵称为“证明”的新号提问哥猜，且问题中故意带有高中生博眼球，涨粉张热度。也不排除有团队背后操作的可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e3.题主真的是天赋异禀，真的证明了这个定理…（当然这种可能不大）\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实我比较怀疑他这篇证明的文章怎么放上来…以这种证明过程难度，没有个几千张纸完不成吧，好害怕他扔个邮箱在这里…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613\" data-hash=\"a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613\"\u003e@Sun Ao\u003c/a\u003e   很真诚的回答。但到达的认知层面决定了看问题的高度和角度，他可能不能完全理解和接受你的想法。毕竟这盘棋已经铺的这么大，，1.1那天是一地鸡毛还是一鸣惊人，都会成为他人生浓墨重彩的一笔。希望提问者看到这个答案\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e我们在这里拭目以待，因为不管他有没有证出，1月1号这天，这个提问都会上知乎首页的\u003c/b\u003e \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=480\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=440\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
